                  <span class="c00">Shameless plug: looking specifically at the Dissemination Phase part, I can&#x27;t help but thinking he would love Code Ocean (<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;codeocean.com" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;codeocean.com</a>). It addresses each of his points:<p>- distribute software (execute with a single click)<p>- reproduce results (published code &amp; data - yours and others&#x27; - is archived with its environment)<p>- collaborate with colleagues (built-in to the system)<p>(Disclaimer: I work at Code Ocean. We&#x27;re in beta.)<span>
